column5: Looks like fishing is on fire again for Lake Ontario ...fished 225 fow today Riggers down 45 to 55 ft 20 ft leads useing Silver Streak Chilli Willie was the hot spoons today also big Braided Dipsys back 85 and 125 on a 3 setting was smashing fish..weather was hot lake was flatt the Flys and Kings & Steelies were biteing .. ;D
Super job fishmaster  Thanks for sharing Leechman
